-->ViewModel vs Android ViewModel(LCDUCU)
Feature				ViewModel											Android ViewModel
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Lifecycle Awareness	Not lifecycle-aware by itself.						Integrated with Android's lifecycle-aware components.
Configuration		Doesn't handle configuration 						Retains data during configuration changes.
					changes like screen rotation automatically.
Dependencies		Framework/platform agnostic.						Depends on Android Jetpack library.
Usage				Common in desktop/web applications 					Used in Android applications.
Context				No context reference								Holds Application context reference
Use Cases			Most UI logic without context requirements			UI logic requiring Application context access